==English==
===Noun===
'''ideogram''' 

# A symbol which represents the idea of something without indicating the sequence of sounds used to pronounce it. Examples include [[numeral]]s, many Chinese characters, [[traffic sign]]s, or graphic symbols such as as [[&]] and [[@]].

